export const types = {
    ADD_PRODUCT: 'sales-counters/add-product',
    REMOVE_PRODUCT: 'sales-counters/remove-product',
    UPDATE_QUANTITY: 'sales-counters/update-count',

    ADD_CUSTOMER: 'sales-counters/add-customer',

    ADD_PAYMENT: 'sales-counters/add-payment',
    UPDATE_PAYMENT: 'sales-counters/update-payment',
    REMOVE_PAYMENT: 'sales-counters/remove-payment',

    ADD_SHIPMENT: 'sales-counters/add-shipment',

    ADD_CUSTOMER_NOTE: 'sales-counters/add-customer-note',
    CHANGE_DELIVERED: 'sales-counters/change-delivered',
    CHANGE_SALE: 'sales-counters/change-sale',

    CHANGE_IS_RESTRICT_ACTION: 'sales-counters/change-is-restrict-action',
    RESET: 'sales-counters/reset',
};
